defaultthe criminal justice bodies defaultwhich exercise functions as 
defaultcriminal justice bodies in that police area, must make arrangements (so far as it is appropriate to do so) for the exercise of functions so as to provide 
defaultan efficient and defaulteffective criminal justice system for the police area.defaultThis is reinstated by the Commissioner's Oath of Office, which unlike the oath on becoming 
